citations.desc: Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at approximately 11:30
am on 13-June-2023.
At approximately 11:30 am the inspector arrived at the facility and spoke to a member of the household who stated that
nobody was available for the inspection. The inspector then left the facility.
End Section
